Summary: Again same White spherical object moving very slow south.
divs: Sighting DetailsAt around 4:58pm on Sunday, November 1st I was outside taking pictures of the natural landscape as I am prone to do when I spotted a white round object moving in the sky at about 88 degrees from the horizon ( North ). The object remained moving south very slow in the sky and I quickly started taking pictures of it. I was able to take 6 pictures in RAW (CR2)and 6 in JPEG before the objet desapear. Strangely enough the object was very similar in appearance to the previous object that I captured on October 11th and October 24 of this year (as reported to the ufo center previously) except that this time it was moving south.
